<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A1404003002" page = "2">
<title>
Adjustment
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Close the valve whose shim (2) is to be replaced by turning crankshaft, then turn tappet (3) till its cut section (1) faces inside as shown in figure.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I2RH0B140006.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.000mm" ver = "01" gw = "165" gh = "128"/>
</figure>
</s1>
