</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1 page = "2">
<ptxt>
Hold tappet at that position using special tool as follows.
</ptxt>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Remove its housing bolts.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Check housing No. and select special tool corresponding to housing No., referring to “Special tool selection table”.
</ptxt>
